                    <span>As a mystery author with my first book in initial release, I have found that reading a wide variety of works helps my writing.  Locke's TWO TREASTISES is one of my favorite books of all time.  Here is the book that subverted absolutism following a glorious revolution.  I read it first as an undergraduate at Claremont McKenna College, and I teach it annually.  Great book.</span>
                  
              
